@amberz.s [τ,τ] @samsamsam__ 
Latest BTC score was calculated at 2025-08-08T12:28:00, ETH score was calculated at 2025-08-08T12:43:00, XAU score was calculated at 2025-08-08T11:55:00, SOL score was calculated at 2025-08-08T12:10:00.
From that time, all scores are not calculating anymore. What is the problem?

@amberz.s [τ,τ] 
Whey are you gonna fix this issue?  There was a same issue 1 month ago. So I mentioned about this issue at that time.
This is a serious issue for miners because there is no update to miners' rankings.

@amberz.s [τ,τ] 
I think we need to adjust `adjustment_alpha ` as original(`18428297329635800000` ) after reg cost rises.
Currently, plz take a look dereg list. miners getting good incentive are in the dereg list. new miners(bad miners) are continuing to reg and old good miners getting incentive are deregging. To prevent this, plz adjust `adjustment_alpha` as original value after reg cost rises high for a while(at lease 4 days). Then, we can identify bad immune miners.

@amberz.s [τ,τ] 
Scoring mechanism has been stopped for 5 hours and there is no changes in the weights of the miners.
All validators are not working now

@amberz.s [τ,τ], The adjustment alpha is reduced to prevent the mass registering but it also means the reg cost can decrease fast.
Whoever does it, he can register over 200 miners for 7 days (immune period) with much cheaper fee.
Should keep the former adjustment alpha and increase the initial register cost significantly against the emission of the subnet.

@Silver Rabbit Synth subnet is designed specially - immune period is 7 days and that must be so long because valis calculate the grade with the past 10 days scores. So immune period must be 7 days at least for immune miners. If immune period is lower than 7 days, immune miners couldnt get incentive during the immune period.
On the other hand, there could be all immune miners for 7 days. So we need to prevent reg competition.
The way to prevent reg competition is just only -  increasing the min_burn

@amberz.s [τ,τ], there are still more registration in the current min_burn
We should keep the situation before the emission is increased, there were only 1 registration a day, even 0, sometimes confident miners reged many.
You should find the way to keep the subnet safe asap
